  <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Vigie gives municipal teams a real-time view of their entire waste collection network. Spot which collection points need emptying on a color-coded map, plan optimized tours with road-accurate routing, manage incidents, and track fleet performance through dedicated dashboards — all in one place.</p>

